Dragon Pact						KEY:Trait ~ Dragon Pact				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.SocialTrait		PREMULT:1,[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.SocialTrait],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Dragon Pact]				SOURCEPAGE:p.3	DESC:Choose one category of true dragon (chromatic, metallic, primal, etc.). You gain a +1 trait bonus on Diplomacy checks against that category of dragon and a +1 trait bonus on Intimidate checks against all creatures of the dragon type that are not of the same category of true dragon.
Drake Anatomist					KEY:Trait ~ Drake Anatomist			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.SocialTrait		PREMULT:1,[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.SocialTrait],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Drake Anatomist]				SOURCEPAGE:p.7	DESC:You gain a +1 trait bonus on damage rolls against creatures with the dragon creature type, and a +2 trait bonus on Knowledge (arcana) checks to identify dragons and their special powers and vulnerabilities.																				ASPECT:CombatBonus|+1 on damage rolls vs. creatures with the dragon creature type.		BONUS:SITUATION|Knowledge (Arcana)=Identify Dragons|1|TYPE=Trait
